## Why This Is Asked
Tests practical rollout discipline for CNFs, multi-region consistency, and robust rollback.

## Key Concepts
- Canary rollouts in CNFs across regions
- Policy drift detection and reconciliation
- Observability with eBPF, traces, and metrics
- Safe rollback criteria and traffic mirroring
- Per-region SLI targets and controlled rollout

## Code Example
```javascript
// Pseudocode: reconcilePolicy(desired, runtime, driftThreshold) 
async function reconcilePolicy(desired, runtime){
  const drift = diff(desired, runtime);
  if(drift > driftThreshold) throw new Error('Policy drift');
  // apply reconciliation
}
```

## Follow-up Questions
- How would you define drift metrics and thresholds for CNFs?
- How would you test rollback reliability under sudden latency spikes?
